WEBVTT

00:00.239 --> 00:03.401
<i>Previously on AMC's
Breaking Bad...</i>

00:03.619 --> 00:07.569
All dead. As is your grandson.

00:07.715 --> 00:11.872
I think Brock may have been poisoned
with something called ricin.

00:12.008 --> 00:15.381
Shut up!
Why did you poison him?

00:15.479 --> 00:19.168
Who do you know? Gus allowed
children to be murdered. Gus!

00:19.376 --> 00:21.235
- I'm gonna kill him.
- Then let me help.

00:26.985 --> 00:29.963
Don't go! Don't go!
No! No!

00:31.000 --> 00:37.074
